OL,5,G1100 Dogs Behaving (Very) Badly
OL,6,     FWarring spaniels Zach and Ollie
OL,7,     Fare spoiling a couple's retirement
OL,8,     Fplans. Can Graeme Hall negotiate a
OL,9,     Fpeace treaty? And amorous
OL,10,     Flabradoodle Rupert is making life
OL,11,     Fhard for a mum.
OL,12,G1200 Dogs Behaving (Very) Badly
OL,13,     FIn the 100th episode, Graeme
OL,14,     Ftackles a canine master food thief
OL,15,     Fwho's pillaging picnics. And an
OL,16,     Fowner's every move is met with an
OL,17,     Fonslaught of barky abuse and nasty
OL,18,     Fnips.
